imdb.plot outline: The series follows amateur and professional couples from Australia, who have found a way to get rich quick. The couples buy homes, renovate and then sell them - all in just a few short weeks. But will it be a successful flip or a disastrous flop?
imdb.title: The Aussie Property Flippers
